The evidence with the title 'NASA, NOAA data show 2016 Warmest year on record globally ... ' says Jan 18, 2017  ... Most of the warming occurred in the past 35 years , with 16 of the 17 warmest years on record occurring since 2001 . Not only was 2016 the warmest year on record , but eight of the 12 months that make up the year – from january through september , with the exception of june – were the warmest on record  ... 
